text:
Looking and hoping for help with the following items, a small list of great kick starters for anyone to help and get rolling with Hyperledger. Our community backlog of bugs and requirements is growing quickly and any help closing out items would be fantastic. Of course members are always available on slack or via the issues to assist. So don’t hesitate to ask for help/guidance/further explanation, and don’t stop here, this is just a quick list of what could be fairly easy items to tackle. Please jump out there on any of these, or others, and thank you for any/all help you can provide! Will add more soon, if this helps. If I’m nuts, I’m ok with you telling me that too :simple_smile:

issue 1077 - Human readable chaincode 
issue 562 - Sample app issuing REST calls to run chaincode
issue 662 - Capture stacktrace on error
issue 617 - Can’t script peer login
issue 724 - Remove existing containers for chaincode if not already connected.
